Package: PPtreeCluster
Type: Package
Title: Cluster Analysis with Projection Pursuit Tree Structure
Version: 2.1.0
Date: 2023-07-12
Authors@R: 
    c(person(given = "Eun-Kyung",
           family = "Lee",
